data.text:
Empire of the Ants is a horror movie directed by Bert Gordon.

Victims[]

Pete - Eaten by the Giant Ants.

Jim - Eaten by the Giant Ants.

Ginny - Eaten by the Giant Ants.

Giant Ant - Exploded by Dan.

Christine Graham - Eaten by the Giant Ants.

Charlie Pearson - Eaten by the Giant Ants.

Dan Stokely - Eaten by the Giant Ants.

Five Engineers - Killed by Giant Ants.

Marilyn Fryser - Eaten by Giant Ants.

58 Giant Ants - Exploded by Joe.

Queen Ant - Exploded by Joe.
